## If you are interested in participating in the workshop this summer please submit the following items to wvinbre.summerbootcamp@gmail.com on or before April 1st:

To participate in this program you must be an undergraduate student currently enrolled in a WV-INBRE partner institution. See the list of participating institutions below.
Early career graduate students or students who have graduated in Spring 2023 will be considered on a case by case basis!

![](wvinbre_partners.png)

